Package: libdleyna-renderer-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libdleyna-renderer-1.0-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: APIs for DMR discovery and manipulation - development files
 dLeyna-renderer provides APIs for discovering and manipulating
 Digital Media Renderers. dLeyna-renderer can be used to implement
 two-box push.
 .
 This package contains the header files for the library and other
 development files.

